title: Craig Wright Is Not Satoshi Nakamoto, Rules UK Court
description: A UK court has ruled that Australian computer scientist Craig Wright, who claims to have invented Bitcoin, is not Satoshi Nakamoto and did not author the Bitcoin whitepaper.
